# Implementation Plan - Main Menu

This plan outlines the steps to create a functional Main Menu for the "Web of Fate" project.

## Goal
Create a `MainMenu` scene with "Start Game", "Settings", and "Quit" buttons that are fully functional.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> I will assume the main game scene is `res://web_of_fate/scenes/simple_web_of_fate.tscn` based on previous exploration. If this is incorrect, please let me know.

## Proposed Changes

### New Scenes & Scripts

#### [NEW] [main_menu.tscn](file:///c:/Users/Lutfi/Desktop/Godot/Assets/simple-card-pile-ui-master/simple-card-pile-ui-master/web_of_fate/scenes/main_menu.tscn)
- A `Control` node based scene.
- **Background**: A `ColorRect` with the existing [bg.gdshader](file:///c:/Users/Lutfi/Desktop/Godot/Assets/simple-card-pile-ui-master/simple-card-pile-ui-master/web_of_fate/scenes/bg.gdshader) for visual consistency.
- **Title**: A `Label` with the game title "Web of Fate".
- **Buttons**: A `VBoxContainer` with:
    - `StartButton`: Changes scene to the main game.
    - `SettingsButton`: Opens the settings menu (or prints a placeholder for now).
    - `QuitButton`: Quits the application.

#### [NEW] [MainMenu.gd](file:///c:/Users/Lutfi/Desktop/Godot/Assets/simple-card-pile-ui-master/simple-card-pile-ui-master/web_of_fate/scripts/MainMenu.gd)
- Script attached to `main_menu.tscn`.
- Handles `pressed` signals from the buttons.
- `_on_start_pressed()`: `get_tree().change_scene_to_file(...)`
- `_on_settings_pressed()`: Toggles visibility of a settings panel (or navigates to settings scene).
- `_on_quit_pressed()`: `get_tree().quit()`

#### [NEW] [settings_menu.tscn](file:///c:/Users/Lutfi/Desktop/Godot/Assets/simple-card-pile-ui-master/simple-card-pile-ui-master/web_of_fate/scenes/settings_menu.tscn)
- A simple placeholder popup for settings.
- Contains a "Back" button to return to the main menu.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1.  **Run the Scene**: Open and run `main_menu.tscn`.
2.  **Test Start**: Click "Start Game" and verify it loads [simple_web_of_fate.tscn](file:///c:/Users/Lutfi/Desktop/Godot/Assets/simple-card-pile-ui-master/simple-card-pile-ui-master/web_of_fate/scenes/simple_web_of_fate.tscn).
3.  **Test Settings**: Click "Settings" and verify it shows the settings panel/scene.
4.  **Test Quit**: Click "Quit" and verify the game closes (note: in editor this just stops the scene).
